trans-unit.source: Provides a designer canvas, which renders the visual representation of a workflow model as it is being designed.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en Spørringsutformer arbeidssonen, som gjengir den visuelle representasjonen av en arbeidsflyt-modell som de blir utformet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext"></xref> object that is a collection of services shared between all elements contained in the designer and used to interact between the host and the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext"> </xref> objekt som er en samling av tjenester delt mellom alle elementer i designer som brukes til å bruke mellom verten og designer.

trans-unit.source: Services are published and requested through the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Services er publisert og forespurt via den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Context is not guaranteed to be available during initialization, as the data binding may have not yet resolved.
trans-unit.target: Konteksten garanteres ikke er tilgjengelig under initialisering, som databindingen har ennå ikke er løst.

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to ensure that an editing context is available.
trans-unit.target: Det er to måter å kontrollere at det finnes en redigering kontekst.

trans-unit.source: - Use <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner.ModelChanged>, which executes whenever the model is assigned to, or when the value the property points to is updated.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner.ModelChanged>, som utfører når modellen er tildelt, eller når verdien for egenskapen peker til er oppdatert.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.WorkflowDesigner.ModelChanged>

trans-unit.source: - Subscribe to the Context dependency property’s availability using <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -Abonnere på den konteksten avhengighetsegenskapen tilgjengelighet i <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A>

trans-unit.source: The editing context for the workflow designer.
trans-unit.target: Redigering konteksten for arbeidsflyten designer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the context menu for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter hurtigmenyen for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The context menu for the designer.
trans-unit.target: Hurtigmenyen for designer.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.DebuggerService"></xref> that is used for run-time debugging.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.DebuggerService"> </xref> som brukes for kjøring feilsøking.

trans-unit.source: An object that implements <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.IDesignerDebugView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.IDesignerDebugView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Saves the current state of the workflow to the <xref:System.WorkflowModel.Design.WorkflowDesigner.Text*> property.
trans-unit.target: Lagrer den gjeldende tilstanden til arbeidsflyten skal den <xref:System.WorkflowModel.Design.WorkflowDesigner.Text*>egenskapen.</xref:System.WorkflowModel.Design.WorkflowDesigner.Text*>

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/add/includes/wfd1-md.md)] is in error state.
trans-unit.target: Angir om den [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/add/includes/wfd1-md.md)] er i feiltilstand.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[wfd2](~/add/includes/wfd2-md.md)] is in error state; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den [!INCLUDE[wfd2](~/add/includes/wfd2-md.md)] er i feil tilstand; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
